{"tid":1687490,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解台灣好多音樂機構都唔承認英國皇家ABRSM考試?","createTime":"2019-11-02T01:21:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T00:55:06.000Z","uid":100680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"24a0eb85599a11adba82a6d0715f1273fbd0e0a5","tid":1687490,"uid":100680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T01:21:10.000Z","msg":"ABRSM唔係世界公認ge咩?<br />\n本人諗住未來去台灣做下音樂演奏或者教育<br />\n但我去台灣PTT論壇查過下<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/man/Musicteach/D48E/M.1085239988.A.23C.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fman%2FMusicteach%2FD48E%2FM.1085239988.A.23C.html&d=rxvDypeE%2FV4%2FTsysNGkz8DizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=2db2ab1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/man/Musicteach/D48E/M.1085239988.A.23C.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/piano/M.1418209557.A.9A3.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2Fpiano%2FM.1418209557.A.9A3.html&d=rxvDypeE%2FV4%2FTsysNGkz8DizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=8f9054a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/piano/M.1418209557.A.9A3.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Musicteach/M.1252048511.A.3DC.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FMusicteach%2FM.1252048511.A.3DC.html&d=rxvDypeE%2FV4%2FTsysNGkz8DizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=7f33b6b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Musicteach/M.1252048511.A.3DC.html</a><br />\n先知原來台灣雖然都係有得考ABRSM，但就算考左，好多台灣音樂機構都唔會承認英國ABRSM所有樂器術科考試<br />\n佢地只會承認佢地自己各間大學的音樂系或者日本YAMAHA公開音樂考試<br />\n<br />\n點解佢地只承認日本或者佢地本土而唔承認英國ABRSM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fdd3e948ea78940a65e18d87ed222d85384e59b","tid":1687490,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T01:40:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EYzJAWY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEYzJAWY